Make a webserver'

Step 1 - set hostname
hostnamectl set-hostname django-server

hostname

>>> django-server

Step 2 - set the host
sudo nano /etc/hosts

add: 139.177.195.251 django-server

Step 3 - add limitied user
sudo adduser michael
>>Adding user `michael' ...
